---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | Tomobil Car Hire">
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-800 text-white py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Our Story</h1>
        <p class="text-xl max-w-2xl">Discover the journey that made Tomobil the leading car hire company.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Company Story -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <div class="prose prose-lg">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Journey</h2>
            <p class="mb-6">
              Founded in 2015, Tomobil started with a simple vision: to make car rental accessible, 
              convenient, and hassle-free for everyone. What began as a small fleet of five cars has 
              now grown into one of the region's most trusted car hire services.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our Mission</h3>
            <p class="mb-6">
              At Tomobil, we're committed to providing exceptional car rental experiences through 
              superior service, premium vehicles, and innovative solutions that exceed our customers' 
              expectations.
            </p>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 my-12">
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Our Values</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-2">
                  <li>• Customer First Approach</li>
                  <li>• Quality & Reliability</li>
                  <li>• Transparency</li>
                  <li>• Innovation</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Key Milestones</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-2">
                  <li>• 2015: Company Founded</li>
                  <li>• 2018: Expanded to 50+ Vehicles</li>
                  <li>• 2020: Launched Digital Platform</li>
                  <li>• 2023: Regional Expansion</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Looking Forward</h3>
            <p>
              As we continue to grow, our commitment to excellence remains unchanged. We're constantly 
              innovating and expanding our services to better serve our customers and maintain our 
              position as a leader in the car hire industry.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
